<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>La Voz del Mercado — Propuesta Estratégica v2</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --black:#0A0A0A;
  --dark:#111111;
  --mid:#181818;
  --card:#1C1C1C;
  --card2:#202020;
  --border:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  --border-a:rgba(255,255,255,0.13);
  --white:#F0F0F0;
  --muted:#6b6b6b;
  --muted2:#909090;
  --violet:#8B5CF6;
  --violet-d:#3F296F;
  --violet-l:rgba(139,92,246,0.10);
  --violet-b:rgba(139,92,246,0.25);
  --orange:#FB923C;
  --orange-l:rgba(251,146,60,0.10);
  --orange-b:rgba(251,146,60,0.25);
  --green-l:rgba(52,211,153,0.10);
  --green-b:rgba(52,211,153,0.22);
  --red-l:rgba(248,113,113,0.08);
  --red-b:rgba(248,113,113,0.2);
  --font:'IBM Plex Sans',sans-serif;
  --mono:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;
}
body{background:var(--black);color:var(--white);font-family:var(--font);font-size:14px;line-height:1.65;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;print-color-adjust:exact}

/* ═══ PAGE ═══ */
.page{max-width:940px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 2.5rem 3rem}

/* ═══ SECTION DIVIDER ═══ */
.sec-divider{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;margin:3.5rem 0 1.75rem}
.sec-divider-line{flex:1;height:.5px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--violet-b),transparent)}
.sec-divider-line-r{flex:1;height:.5px;background:linear-gradient(270deg,var(--violet-b),transparent)}
.sec-label{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;white-space:nowrap}
.sec-n{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--violet);font-weight:500}
.sec-t{font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;letter-spacing:-.01em}
.sec-tag{font-size:10px;font-family:var(--mono);color:var(--muted);border:.5px solid var(--border-a);padding:3px 9px;border-radius:4px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em}

/* ═══ HEADER ═══ */
.doc-header{padding-bottom:2.5rem;border-bottom:.5px solid var(--border-a);margin-bottom:.5rem}
.header-top{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:2rem}
.logo-area{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px}
.logo-img{height:44px;object-fit:contain}
.dot-sep{width:4px;height:4px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--border-a)}
.programa-tag{font-size:11px;font-family:var(--mono);color:var(--muted2);letter-spacing:.08em}
.doc-h1{font-size:44px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.025em;line-height:1.05;color:#fff;margin-bottom:.5rem}
.doc-h1 em{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--violet) 0%,#a78bfa 100%);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;font-style:normal}
.doc-sub{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted2);max-width:580px;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:2rem}
.header-meta{display:flex;gap:0;flex-wrap:wrap;border:.5px solid var(--border-a);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden}
.meta-item{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px;padding:.85rem 1.25rem;border-right:.5px solid var(--border-a);flex:1;min-width:110px}
.meta-item:last-child{border-right:none}
.meta-lbl{font-size:9px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--muted);font-family:var(--mono)}
.meta-val{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--white)}

/* ═══ VISION BLOCK ═══ */
.vision-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(63,41,111,.5) 0%,rgba(63,41,111,.2) 100%);border:.5px solid rgba(139,92,246,.35);border-radius:12px;padding:2rem 2.25rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:12px}
.vision-wrap::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:-80px;right:-80px;width:280px;height:280px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(139,92,246,.08);pointer-events:none}
.vision-wrap::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:-60px;left:-60px;width:200px;height:200px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(139,92,246,.05);pointer-events:none}
.v-chip{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:10px;font-family:var(--mono);letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#a78bfa;background:rgba(139,92,246,.15);border:.5px solid rgba(139,92,246,.3);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:100px;margin-bottom:1rem}
.vision-wrap p{font-size:15px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.8;color:#ddd6fe;position:relative;z-index:1}
.vision-wrap strong{color:#fff;font-weight:600}

/* ═══ CARDS ═══ */
.card{background:var(--mid);border:.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:1.25rem 1.5rem}
.card-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:10px}
.card-sm{background:var(--card);border:.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:1rem 1.25rem}
.ca{border-color:var(--violet-b);background:var(--violet-l)}
.co{border-color:var(--orange-b);background:var(--orange-l)}
.cg{border-color:var(--green-b);background:var(--green-l)}
.cr{border-color:var(--red-b);background:var(--red-l)}

/* ═══ PILLS ═══ */
.pill{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:10px;font-weight:500;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:100px;font-family:var(--mono);white-space:nowrap}
.pv{background:var(--violet-l);color:#c4b5fd;border:.5px solid var(--violet-b)}
.po{background:var(--orange-l);color:#fdba74;border:.5px solid var(--orange-b)}
.pg{background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);color:var(--muted2);border:.5px solid var(--border-a)}
.pgr{background:var(--green-l);color:#6ee7b7;border:.5px solid var(--green-b)}
.pr{background:var(--red-l);color:#fca5a5;border:.5px solid var(--red-b)}
.pill-dot{width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:currentColor;opacity:.7}

/* ═══ FUNCTIONS ROW ═══ */
.fn-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:10px;margin-top:12px}
.fn-card{background:var(--card);border:.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:1.1rem 1.25rem}
.fn-emoji{font-size:20px;margin-bottom:.5rem;display:block}
.fn-title{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;margin-bottom:4px}
.fn-desc{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted2);line-height:1.6}
.fn-new{border-color:var(--orange-b);background:var(--orange-l)}

/* ═══ FORMATO STATS ═══ */
.stat-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:0;border:.5px solid var(--border-a);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden}
.stat-cell{padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;border-right:.5px solid var(--border-a)}
.stat-cell:last-child{border-right:none}
.stat-lbl{font-size:9px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--muted);font-family:var(--mono);margin-bottom:4px}
.stat-n{font-size:28px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.1}
.stat-n em{color:var(--violet);font-style:normal}
.stat-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted2);margin-top:4px;line-height:1.5}
.stat-note{padding: 20px 0px;margin-top:20px;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted2);line-height:1.65}
.stat-note strong{color:var(--white);font-weight:600}

/* ═══ TIMELINE / RUNDOWN ═══ */
.rundown{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0}
.rd-row{display:flex;gap:0;align-items:stretch}
.rd-time-col{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;min-width:64px;padding-right:1rem}
.rd-time{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:500;color:var(--violet);white-space:nowrap;padding-top:3px}
.rd-dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--violet);border:2px solid var(--black);margin-top:4px;flex-shrink:0;position:relative;z-index:1}
.rd-dot-o{background:var(--orange)}
.rd-dot-g{background:#34d399}
.rd-line{width:1.5px;flex:1;background:var(--border-a);margin-top:2px;min-height:12px}
.rd-content{flex:1;padding-bottom:1.5rem;padding-top:1px}
.rd-label{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;margin-bottom:3px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.rd-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted2);line-height:1.65}
.rd-end .rd-line{display:none}

/* ═══ PILARES ═══ */
.pilar-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:10px}
.pilar-card{background:var(--card);border:.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:1.1rem 1.25rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.5rem}
.pilar-top{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;gap:.5rem}
.pilar-emoji{font-size:18px;flex-shrink:0;line-height:1}
.pilar-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#fff}
.pilar-desc{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--muted2);line-height:1.65}
.pilar-new{border-color:var(--orange-b);background:var(--orange-l)}
.pilar-serie{border-color:var(--violet-b);background:var(--violet-l)}

/* ═══ IDEA BOX ═══ */
.idea{border-radius:8px;padding:1.1rem 1.25rem;margin-top:10px}
.idea-o{background:var(--orange-l);border:.5px solid var(--orange-b)}
.idea-r{background:var(--red-l);border:.5px solid var(--red-b)}
.idea-g{background:var(--violet-l);border:.5px solid var(--violet-b)}
.chip-g{color:var(--muted2)}
.gd{color:rgba(180,180,180,.85)}
.idea-v{background:var(--violet-l);border:.5px solid var(--violet-b)}
.idea-chip{font-size:9px;font-family:var(--mono);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:6px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.chip-o{color:var(--orange)}
.chip-r{color:#f87171}
.chip-v{color:#a78bfa}
.idea-t{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;margin-bottom:3px}
.idea-d{font-size:11.5px;line-height:1.65}
.od{color:rgba(253,186,116,.8)}
.rd{color:rgba(252,165,165,.75)}
.vd{color:rgba(196,181,253,.8)}

/* ═══ DIAS GRILLA ═══ */
.guest-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:10px}
.dia-card{background:var(--card);border:.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:1.1rem 1.25rem}
.dia-head{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;margin-bottom:.85rem}
.dia-emoji{font-size:16px}
.dia-n{font-size:11px;font-family:var(--mono);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;color:var(--violet);font-weight:500}
.dia-row{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--muted2);padding:4px 0;border-bottom:.5px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:7px;line-height:1.5}
.dia-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.dia-b{color:var(--violet);font-size:9px;margin-top:3px;flex-shrink:0}

/* ═══ TESTS ═══ */
.test-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}
.test-item{display:flex;gap:1.25rem;align-items:stretch;background:var(--card);border:.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:0;overflow:hidden;transition:border-color .2s}
.test-item:hover{border-color:var(--violet-b)}
.t-n-col{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-width:48px;background:rgba(139,92,246,.08);border-right:.5px solid var(--border);padding:.75rem .5rem;flex-shrink:0}
.t-n{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:18px;font-weight:600;color:var(--violet);line-height:1}
.t-n-sub{font-size:8px;font-family:var(--mono);color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;margin-top:2px}
.t-body{padding:1rem 1.25rem;flex:1}
.t-lbl{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;margin-bottom:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.t-d{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--muted2);line-height:1.65}

/* ═══ PRODUCER ═══ */
.prod-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr;gap:10px}
.checklist{display:flex;flex-direction:column}
.chk{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted2);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:.5px solid var(--border);line-height:1.6}
.chk:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.chk-v{color:var(--violet);font-size:11px;margin-top:2px;flex-shrink:0;font-family:var(--mono)}

/* ═══ PREPRODUCCION ═══ */
.prep-timeline{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0}
.prep-row{display:flex;gap:1.5rem;align-items:flex-start;padding:.85rem 1rem;border-bottom:.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px}.prep-row:nth-child(odd){background:rgba(255,255,255,.025)}
.prep-row:last-child{border-bottom:none;padding-bottom:0}
.prep-day{min-width:90px;font-size:11px;font-family:var(--mono);color:var(--violet);font-weight:500;padding-top:2px;line-height:1.7;flex-shrink:0}
.prep-title{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;margin-bottom:3px}
.prep-desc{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--muted2);line-height:1.65}

/* ═══ TECH ═══ */
.tech-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:10px}
.tech-card{background:var(--card);border:.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:1.25rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:border-color .2s}
.tech-card:hover{border-color:var(--border-a)}
.tech-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:-30px;right:-30px;width:80px;height:80px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(139,92,246,.05);pointer-events:none}
.tech-card.tc-pri{border-color:var(--violet-b);background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(63,41,111,.3) 0%,var(--card) 70%)}
.tech-title{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;border-bottom:.5px solid var(--border);padding-bottom:8px}
.tech-d{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted2);font-family:var(--mono);line-height:2}

/* ═══ NEXT STEPS / ROADMAP ═══ */
.steps-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:10px}
.step-card{background:var(--card);border:.5px solid var(--border);border-left:2px solid var(--violet-b);border-radius:8px;padding:1.1rem 1.25rem;display:flex;gap:.75rem;align-items:flex-start;transition:border-color .2s}.step-card:hover{border-left-color:var(--violet)}
.step-who{font-size:10px;font-family:var(--mono);color:var(--violet);font-weight:500;min-width:56px;padding-top:2px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em}
.step-what{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--muted2);line-height:1.6}
.roadmap-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:10px;margin-top:12px}
.rm-card{background:var(--card);border:.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:1.1rem 1.25rem}
.rm-phase{font-size:9px;font-family:var(--mono);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;margin-bottom:.6rem;font-weight:500}
.rm-phase-1{color:#34d399}
.rm-phase-2{color:var(--orange)}
.rm-phase-3{color:var(--violet)}
.rm-title{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;margin-bottom:.5rem}
.rm-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px}
.rm-item{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted2);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:6px;line-height:1.5}
.rm-dot{width:4px;height:4px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:5px}
.dot-g{background:#34d399}
.dot-o{background:var(--orange)}
.dot-v{background:var(--violet)}

/* ═══ COMPETENCIA ═══ */
.comp-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:10px}
.comp-card{background:var(--card);border:.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:1.1rem 1.25rem}
.comp-prog{font-size:10px;font-family:var(--mono);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:5px}
.comp-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;margin-bottom:.5rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.comp-detail{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted2);line-height:1.65}
.comp-vs{margin-top:.6rem;padding-top:.6rem;border-top:.5px solid var(--border);font-size:11px;color:rgba(139,92,246,.9);line-height:1.5}

/* ═══ UTILS ═══ */
.mt1{margin-top:.75rem}
.mt2{margin-top:1.25rem}
.strong{font-weight:600;color:#fff}
.text-m{color:var(--muted2);font-size:12px;line-height:1.65}

/* ═══ FOOTER ═══ */
.doc-footer{border-top:.5px solid var(--border-a);padding-top:2rem;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:1rem;margin-top:3rem}
.f-l,.f-r{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);font-family:var(--mono);line-height:1.9}
.f-r{text-align:right}
.f-brand{color:var(--violet)}

/* ═══ ACCENT LINES ═══ */
.accent-line{height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--violet-b),transparent);margin:2rem 0}

@media print{
  body{background:#0A0A0A!important}
  .page{padding:1.5rem}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

<!-- ██████ HEADER ██████ -->
<div class="doc-header">
  <div class="header-top">
    <div class="logo-area" style="flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px">
      <p style="font-size:16px;font-weight:400;color:#6b6b6b;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-top:8px">Propuesta estratégica</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h1 class="doc-h1">La Voz del<br><em>Mercado</em></h1>
  <p class="doc-sub">Transformación hacia el programa financiero de referencia del ecosistema Bitcoin hispanohablante. Estructura profesional, producción real, comunidad activa.</p>

  <div class="header-meta">
    <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-lbl">Preparado por</span><span class="meta-val">Thiago Suarez</span></div>
    <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-lbl">Conductor</span><span class="meta-val">Carlos Maslatón</span></div>
    <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-lbl">Frecuencia</span><span class="meta-val">Lun / Mier / Vier</span></div>
    <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-lbl">Horario</span><span class="meta-val">11:00 – 12:00 ARG</span></div>
    <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-lbl">Idioma</span><span class="meta-val">Español · Latam</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ██████ 01 VISIÓN ██████ -->
<div class="sec-divider"><div class="sec-divider-line"></div><div class="sec-label"><span class="sec-n">01</span><span class="sec-t">Visión del programa</span></div><div class="sec-divider-line-r"></div><span class="sec-tag">estrategia</span></div>

<div class="vision-wrap">
  <div class="v-chip">🎯 Posicionamiento</div>
  <p>La Voz del Mercado deja de ser un análisis de pantalla con un conductor solo y se convierte en el <strong>programa financiero de referencia del ecosistema Bitcoin hispanohablante</strong>. El modelo es Luzu / Olga / CocoCap. La referencia de industria es Bull Market con su canal de streaming — pero llevado a otro nivel: Bitcoin-native, con análisis en BTC y posicionamiento institucional.</p>
</div>

<div class="fn-grid">
  <div class="fn-card">
    <span class="fn-emoji">📊</span>
    <p class="fn-title">Informar &amp; entretener</p>
    <p class="fn-desc">Contenido financiero real con autoridad y opinión fundada. Sin condescendencia, sin hype vacío. El programa que el Bitcoiner hispanohablante no tiene.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="fn-card">
    <span class="fn-emoji">🏛️</span>
    <p class="fn-title">Posicionar Roxom</p>
    <p class="fn-desc">Cada emisión es un vehículo de marca medible. Roxom como el mercado de capitales Bitcoin de referencia en Latam. No un anuncio — una demostración.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="fn-card">
    <span class="fn-emoji">🔬</span>
    <p class="fn-title">Laboratorio de audiencia ★</p>
    <p class="fn-desc">Testeo en tiempo real de mensajes y productos de Roxom. La reacción del chat informa campañas antes de escalarlas. Cada stream es un focus group gratuito.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ██████ REFERENCIA BULLMARKET ██████ -->
